  "body": "We now have pretty structured way of validating api object, but the error message to end user is not descriptive, e.g. when creating a replication controller with restart policy 'never', we get:\n\n```\nspec.template.restartPolicy: invalid value '{<nil> <nil> 0xe68308}\n```\n\neven as simple as label name, we shouldn't assume end-user is familiar with our requirement.\n\nApart from what is wrong, we'd better also give why it is wrong.\n",
